high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the wall.
Pick up the toilet plunger that is on the floor next to the toilet.
Turn to the left and face the cabinets.
Open the cabinet on the right and put the plunger inside of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: To put the plunger inside the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around to face the toilet and turn left to face the towel rack.
Look to the floor and grab the plunger from the floor.
Turn around and turn right to face the bathroom sink.
Open the cabinet door to place the plunger inside and close the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Place the plunger into the cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the left side of the toilet next to the plunger
Pick up the plunger on the floor that is to the left of the toilet
Carry the plunger to the sink on the right hand side
Place the plunger inside of the white cupboard under the right sink
anns.task_desc: Move a plunger from the toilet to the bathroom cupboard
